Format: Verse
By: Hafiz
Title: Certainty
Description: January 25
---
From man’s perspective in this extraordinary game of life

it is so easy to become confused and think you are the doer,

but from God’s infinite certainty He always knows

He is the only One who should ever be put on trial.
